  "text": "Differential scanning calorimetry (DSC) experiments were performed in a VP-DSC instrument from Microcal INC. as described previously. Fourier transform infrared spectroscopy (FTIR) and Thioflavine T (ThT) fluorescence growth curves experimental details were also carried out as it is referred in previous references [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] .",
